.SH NAME
jtutil-drop1 \- Drop one byte out of two from stdin
.SH DESCRIPTION
Use this command when you need to separate a 16\-bit memory into two 8\-bit halves.
By default, it outputs the higher byte of each 16\-bit word
.SS "Usage:"
.IP
